        <mxCell id="EbJcEXxP2qamZhwfHy2c-156" parent="1" style="shape=note;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#ffffcc;strokeColor=#cccc00;fontSize=10;size=14;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4;" value="&lt;b&gt;Data Flow Example (Step 7):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. User turns ASV1 encoder on ESP32&lt;br&gt;2. SingularityManager receives &amp;quot;E3 = -45&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;3. ESP32InputBridge → InputState.Set(&amp;quot;ASV1&amp;quot;, 75)&lt;br&gt;4. SOPManager evaluates step 7 conditions&lt;br&gt;5. TimingValidator: only 2s elapsed (need 4s) X&lt;br&gt;6. After 4s+ and ASV1=50%: all conditions met&lt;br&gt;7. PipeColorManager: left-of-NRV1 → LightGreen&lt;br&gt;8. ChecklistUI: enables &amp;quot;Next Step&amp;quot; button&lt;br&gt;9. User presses button → advance to step 8&lt;br&gt;10. Pipe colors reset for new step targets" vertex="1">
